    "content": "<p>Parts P1 - P7 are machined first on a milling machine and then polished at a separate machine. Using the information in the following table, the minimum total completion time required for carrying out both the operations for all 7 parts is _______ hours.</p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:17px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\"><strong>Part</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:17px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\"><strong>Milling (hours)</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:17px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\"><strong>Polishing (hours)</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:18px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">P1</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:18px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">8</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:18px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">6</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:18px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">P2</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:18px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">3</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:18px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">2</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:17px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">P3</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:17px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">3</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:17px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">4</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:18px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">P4</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:18px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">4</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:18px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">6</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:17px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">P5</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:17px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">5</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:17px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">7</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:18px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">P6</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:18px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">6</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:18px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">4</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:18px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">P7</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:18px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">2</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:68px;height:18px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">1</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n",
